Package net.dean.jraw.models

Contains "model" classes: That is, they represent a data structure returned from the API.

See: Description

Package net.dean.jraw.models Description

Contains "model" classes: That is, they represent a data structure returned from the API. Most classes will extend JsonModel, but they are not required to.
